1>  Regular Consumers - 
normal people who buy exotic produce occasionally for household use will be our first customers. Considering the typical Indian consumer mindset these customers will buy our products which sell cheaper than currently existing alternatives moreover with the advantage of vertical farming our products are in the market throughout the year

2>  Industries - 
Industries - When we have penetrated a satisfactory portion of other customer segments we wish to target industries like pharmaceutical, manufacturing, beverages etc

3>  Food Chains - 
This segment includes restaurants and food chains having contracts with us where we supply our products again at a cheaper rate and throughout the year , With us this segment and utilize exotic ingredients in all-seasons 
